sets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都同意需要一定既正能量先可以繼續落去<br />\n但又唔可以太多<br />\n<br />\n不過其實有時連登太負 去返fb即刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFb啲留言好正面 有鼓勵作用"},{"pid":"a313312109ee8f4720dcb6ef144fbca7ed0ed865","tid":1764034,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T20:53:35.000Z","msg":"人權法通過左 區選大勝<br />\n班黑警高官紅官等死啦哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n脫離現實的樂園係冇意義<br />\n<br />\n我只可以話唔好見到有人比人拉左告暴動罪就覺得佢地犧牲左前途<br />\n我地越快贏 佢地的損失就越細 而且我地將來會補償佢的損失(假設佢未死的話)<br />\n比起樂觀撚<br />\n我認為仇恨撚更重要<br />\n煽動人仇恨警察 仇恨高官 仇恨法官<br />\n越仇恨一個人 自然會對佢越冇同情心<br />\n對敵人冇同情心係好事 對敵人有同情心係好危險的事"},{"pid":"43700b04c44f74defb738fb1ad604cf0ade28ce7","tid":1764034,"uid":17719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T22:37:37.000Z","msg":"係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35394e4db9222e0ccaa72db9c8a84210aad2077","tid":1764034,"uid":176996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T22:43:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3e2c952c60b673e342de8f637b38d690b0230ab2","tid":1764034,"uid":35309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T23:04:29.000Z","msg":"正能量！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a8b4daa43d4d54c8bc7e9d4d162e88a4ff6c06","tid":1764034,"uid":220182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b6e3d18326011a024ac593669be286631a7191f","tid":1764034,"uid":146055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ab22e66086e8c76bcbb483c44b194206aa64e95","tid":1764034,"uid":220182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64b6bde59be1edd4b2410d991c50056286ca89f6","tid":1764034,"uid":146055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T20:07:01.000Z","msg":"屌 咁究竟邊張先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr